        <h2 id="recipe-noodles">Noodles</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 10 minutes </li>
            <li>Serves: 2 members</li>
        </ul>
        
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingredients</th>
                    <th>Quantity</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Noodles</td>
                    <td>1 pack</td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>Red chilli</td>
                    <td> <sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub> spoon</td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>Salt</td>
                    <td>1 spoon</td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>Tomatoes</td>
                    <td>2 units</td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>Potato</td>
                    <td>1 Unit</td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>Tomato sauce</td>
                    <td>As per needed</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Take a whole pack of noodles.<br>
        <b>Step 2:</b> Drop the noodles in 3 glass of water in a cooker.<br>
        <b>Step 3:</b>Take a pan place it on stove.<br>
        <b>Step 4:</b>Put some oil on the stove.<br>
        <b>Step 5:</b>Increase the flame.<br>
        <b>Step 6:</b>Cut the tomatoes and place it over the pan.<br>
        <b>Step 7:</b>Let it fry for 2 miniutes.<br>
        <b>Step 8:</b>Cut the potatoes.<br>
        <b>Step 9:</b>Fry it for 2 miniutes.<br>
        <b>Step 10:</b>Now cook the noodles till the cooker whistled for 1 time and then soak the water in the cooker.<br>
        <b>Step 11:</b>Now mix the masala along with oil (tomatoes & potatoes)<br>
        <b>Step 12:</b>Now cook it for  miniutes.<br>
        <b>Step 13:</b>Your noodles are ready serve it with tomato sauce eat it.
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/75/Misua_noodles.jpg"alt="Noodles image" width="300">
            
        </p>
        
